 fro through the earth: and he said, Get you hence, walk to and fro through the earth. So they walked to and fro through the earth.","year":-519},{"id":"rechdYhKkqRGGfxy1","ref":"Zech.6.8","text":"Then cried he upon me, and spake unto me, saying, Behold, these that go toward the north country have quieted my spirit in the north country.","year":-519}]}
